CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 13, 1959, pg. 1, reads: "Please Help Them - Mr. and Mrs. Robert Tyler and their six children, who are being forced to move from a tinder-box house at 2817 Berthoud St., are in extreme mental anguish this week because they have no place to move. Can you help them? - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Tyler family, including Robert Tyler, Mrs. Tyler, and their six children, gathered on porch of house, 2817 Berthoud Street, Hill District
